title: Helmut Lachenmann - Das Madchen mit den Schwefelholzern
description:
No hits for Helmut Lachenmann? well, time for a change.

Here you have a complete pack of Helmut&#039;s only opera, The Little Match Girl.

It&#039;s contents are:

1. 367 photographs of the manuscript full score published by Breitkopf & Hertel.

2. Kairos label double CD, Staatsoper Stuttgart conducted by Lothar Zagrosek.  

3. ECM label double CD, SWR Sinfonieorchester conducted by Sylvain Cambreling.


    Enjoy and Seed!
